Package de.k3b.geo.io.gpx Description

This Package defines Android independant code to handle *.gpx files with locations/trackpoints.

  • GeoPointDto:
    • a location or trackpoint that can be represented in a gpx file.
  • GpxFormatter:
    • Formats GeoPointDto-s or ILocation-s as geo-xml.
  • GpxReader, GpxReaderBase, GeoXmlOrTextParser:
    • reads GeoPointDto from file or stream.
